{"tid":1657304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英、德、日、台版人權法案","createTime":"2019-10-16T04:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T05:11:55.000Z","uid":270374,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b5e05dacc1401ceca0ab00cfc2449f78db52c60d","tid":1657304,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:35:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英、德、日、台版人權法案</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以海外活動來說，300萬不算多，大家考慮下。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=45e17e9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/</a><br />\n<br />\n新一階段工作為期兩年，除繼續經營美國網絡外，我們亦將集中德國、英國、日本、台灣等四大重點國家，拓展我們的連結及遊說網絡，當中德國是過去多次就人權問題發聲的歐盟成員國之一、英國是《中英聯合聲明》簽署國、台灣則同樣是威權中國下的命運共同體，而日本乃東亞最具軟實力、近年相當關注中國影響的國家。<br />\n<br />\n新一階段國際遊說工作為期兩年，眾籌金額300萬，包括：<br />\n【海外網絡】資助海外港人進行遊說，在重點國家建立長期遊說網絡（約50萬）<br />\n【主動外訪】針對外國國會及政府機關，主動出擊進行策略性外訪（約100萬）【🔎訪港考察】邀請議員及社運組織來港考察，壯大香港與其他公民社會（約50萬）<br />\n【研究團隊】聘請本地研究團隊，為遊說及倡議工作提供法律研究和研究支援（約100萬）"},{"pid":"891b369fa4036af12735724a7c2e7f47c061052d","tid":1657304,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:36:09.000Z","msg":"1020 到時見!<br />\n<br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去[2]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657270</a>"},{"pid":"781ea52ba597fe8e4f2de5dddcae90e17ca1663f","tid":1657304,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"ef990cf17f1f970f891f2a8b64cc4d3a6dcfc7d3","tid":1657304,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:47:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7ba8ddb485f18cfddb300842592d9d65f8cad84c","tid":1657304,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8542614fcc556f90ef58f06e12225ec49d833c6d","tid":1657304,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"756dca186da0bb478ba42d3ca97ca80814c49d9b","tid":1657304,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:55:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d28cbeea01e9225cc223aeafa5d593a00fe39c58","tid":1657304,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"台灣自己都未顧得掂 仲叫佢去挑釁中國<br />\n<br />\n而且d狗官狗賊 無乜人有資產仔女係台灣 簡直無威脅<br />\n<br />\n用d時間去 <br />\n<br />\n英國 《&mdash;&mdash;一大堆英籍係香港 <br />\n<br />\n加拿大 澳洲 同德國啦 緊係"},{"pid":"073a2fd11e6b01204039a1b4149fc9e584beb59c","tid":1657304,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:03:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56f20d05f93f88cb2b1b05473943f2d13a3ebd67","tid":1657304,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d924c3ca92b062ffa80850794bd6f1e021162c55","tid":1657304,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:06:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b924f64e8b11f5551e6e8ee517f9da31d43142","tid":1657304,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":